column1: # LeBauer, David, Michael Dietze, Rob Kooper, Steven Long, Patrick Mulrooney, Gareth Scott Rohde, Dan Wang (2010).  Biofuel Ecophysiological Traits and Yields Database (BETYdb), Energy Biosciences Institute, University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign. doi:10.13012/J8H41PB9 All public data in BETYdb is made available under the Open Data Commons Attribution License (ODC-By) v1.0. You are free to share, create, and adapt its contents. Data with an access_level field and value <= 2 is is not covered by this license but may be available for use with consent.

column2: SELECT "traits_and_yields_view".* FROM "traits_and_yields_view"  WHERE (traits_and_yields_view.access_level >= 4) AND ((LOWER(sitename) LIKE LOWER('%cassava%') OR LOWER(city) LIKE LOWER('%cassava%') OR LOWER(scientificname) LIKE LOWER('%cassava%') OR LOWER(commonname) LIKE LOWER('%cassava%') OR LOWER(author) LIKE LOWER('%cassava%') OR LOWER(trait) LIKE LOWER('%cassava%') OR LOWER(trait_description) LIKE LOWER('%cassava%') OR citation_year::text = 'cassava') AND (LOWER(sitename) LIKE LOWER('%a_biomass%') OR LOWER(city) LIKE LOWER('%a_biomass%') OR LOWER(scientificname) LIKE LOWER('%a_biomass%') OR LOWER(commonname) LIKE LOWER('%a_biomass%') OR LOWER(author) LIKE LOWER('%a_biomass%') OR LOWER(trait) LIKE LOWER('%a_biomass%') OR LOWER(trait_description) LIKE LOWER('%a_biomass%') OR citation_year::text = 'a_biomass')) AND (checked >= 1)
